OL,3,CCalls to update 'narrow and
OL,4,Cinflexible' rules on sanctioning
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FThere are calls for tougher sanctions
OL,8,Fagainst politicians who break Jersey's
OL,9,FStates Assembly code of conduct.
OL,11,FRaluca Kovacs, a Deputy St. Saviour,
OL,12,Fwants the Privileges and Procedures
OL,13,FCommittee (PPC) to review, and where
OL,14,Fappropriate, amend Standing Orders
OL,15,Frelating to breaches of the code of
OL,16,Fconduct.
