OL,3,CCalls to update 'narrow and
OL,4,Cinflexible' rules on sanctioning
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FIt comes just days ahead of a debate
OL,8,Fon whether Deputy Philip Ozouf should
OL,9,Fbe suspended from office for a second
OL,10,Ftime after admitting offences linked
OL,11,Fto the employment of Rwandan nationals.
OL,13,FDespite increasing pressure from both
OL,14,Ffellow politicians and the public,
OL,15,FDeputy Ozouf has refused to resign.
OL,17,FThe PPC only has powers to suspend a
OL,18,FStates member, and there is no
OL,19,Fmechanism to remove one. Deputy Kovacs
OL,20,Fsays the current system is narrow and
OL,21,Finflexible and needs to be reviewed.
