OL,7,FIssues Deputy Kovacs has asked to be
OL,8,Freviewed:
OL,10,FThe scope and variety of sanctions:
OL,11,FCurrently, a States members can only
OL,12,Fbe suspended- there is no mechanism to
OL,13,Fexpel a politician from the assembly.
OL,15,FRecall Mechanisms: A recall mechanism
OL,16,Fwould allow voters to remove a Member
OL,17,Fin specific, serious circumstances,
OL,18,Freinforcing accountability.
