OL,7,FAppeals and procedural fairness: PPC
OL,8,Fwould need to determine whether
OL,9,FMembers should have access to a formal
OL,10,Fappeal process and balance fairness
OL,11,Fwith the need for decisive
OL,12,Fdisciplinary action.
OL,14,FDefinition of "Serious" vs "Minor"
OL,15,FBreach: Clear criteria are needed to
OL,16,Fdistinguish minor breaches
OL,17,F(potentially dealt with more
OL,18,Finformally) from serious ones
OL,19,Frequiring formal sanctions.
