OL,7,FAlignment with Other Jurisdictions:
OL,8,FOther parliaments use broader
OL,9,Fsanctions, including warnings,
OL,10,Fmandatory apologies, suspension of
OL,11,Fprivileges, and recall.
OL,13,FDeputy Kovacs says: "Recent events
OL,14,Fhave highlighted the importance of re-
OL,15,Fexamining sanctions to ensure thatJthe
OL,16,Fsanctions framework is fair, flexible
OL,17,Fand proportionate for minor and
OL,18,Fserious breaches."
