OL,7,FDeputy of St Saviour, Malcolm Ferey,
OL,8,Fsays they have yet to receive a
OL,9,Frequete, but he says: "It seems the
OL,10,Frequete would exclude the deputy from
OL,11,Fthe parish Hall, and I would question
OL,12,Fsome of the legalities around doing
OL,13,Fthat in a public building."
OL,15,FHe adds: "Parishioners have a right to
OL,16,Fbring a requete, it's people power,
OL,17,Fand we have a duty to consider that
OL,18,Frequete, and indeed to bring it to a
OL,19,Fparish assembly."
